title: Betron Clear Silicone Case Back Cover for Samsung Galaxy Note 10
description: Betron Ultra-Thin clear Silicone TPU Gel Case compatible with Samsung Galaxy Note 10. With a slim-line silicone TPU gel body to ensure minimum weight and optimal protection,case is the best unobtrusive and lightweight option for protecting your new smartphone from damage. With a clear gel body, this case is extremely stylish and allows you to preserve the unique look of your Phone while still providing maximum protection to the interior and exterior of your new smartphone.An Excellent Degree of Protection. This cover is extremely easy to fit; simply slot it around the back of your phone and ensure it is firmly in place. Once fitted, the rubberized case provides an excellent degree of protection from scratches, scuffs, drops, scrapes and dents, as well as providing a barrier against impacts and the damage they can cause. Handy Ports, Cut-Outs and Buttons .The case comes equipped with a number of handy cut-out ports and button moulds, enabling easy access to all external features of the Mobile including the headphone jack, charger port, camera, power button and volume controls for ease of use.Compatible with the Samsung Galaxy Note 10 only Raised camera and screen bezels help protect against scratches Subtle microdot pattern prevents the wet, clinging look common among clear cases, keeping your Galaxy Note 10 looking great Durable polymer and reinforced corners team up to protect your Samsung Note 10 from drops & other impacts. Thin to 0.04inch, gives a snug fit making you feel like holding the bare phone but with more grip. Flexible resilient soft design, just a breeze to apply, makes your new Phone stay cosy with care, also a breeze to put on or off
